data.description: Presenting the perfect little starter home! Or Snowbird nest! Newer Build, 2021 in clean, well-kept community with good land space (½ acre) near town and all its conveniences and the Ocala National Forest. Ocala is the perfect setting to enjoy the best of Florida's rolling pastures and scenic springs, this is a wonderful place to call home while enjoy nature’s playground.  Home is Beautiful, light and bright with large rooms and ample utility / laundry area. New backyard Gazebo for outside enjoyment. These 3-bedroom 2-bath mobile home has over 1800 square feet of living area split bedroom plan with large walk-in closet, Tub – Shower. Some furniture is available for sale.
